        "timestamp": "2017-09-08 18:58:39.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\nJohnson, \n\nThe following instructions are missing in v_gw_install.sh, v_bng_install.sh and v_gmux_install.sh:\n\nINSTALL_PACKAGE_REPO_URL=$(cat /opt/config/install_package_repo_url.txt)\nINSTALL_PACKAGE_REPO_BRANCH=$(cat /opt/config/install_package_repo_branch.txt)\n\nIn those files, INSTALL_PACKAGE_REPO_URL and INSTALL_PACKAGE_REPO_BRANCH aren't set. Could you please update the commit?\n\nAlso, I see that you removed the Apache2 installation part from v_web_install.sh. What do you plan to use in that VM?\n\nThanks,\nMarco",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "6f50679c0c0582becf053b64b67fb1edcc13c090",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 55,
          "name": "Marco Platania",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "platania@research.att.com",
          "username": "platania"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2017-09-12 14:23:11.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nAlso, I've noticed that in the *_install.sh script you clone the demo repo in this way:\n\ngit clone http://gerrit.onap.org/r/demo.git -b vBNG/vBRG/VG/...\n\nThis assumes the existence of vBNG/vBRG/VG/... branches, while we should have only release-X.Y.Z and master branches.\n\nMarco",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
